name: 贾罗德·林齐
introduction: Jarod (defined as "spear strong" in Greek and "ruler, he who descends" in Hebrew) is an American actor and musician born in New Jersey. Known for his distinct, low-resonating bass voice that is not to be ignored.He has appeared on the hit NBC spin-off series 'Law & Order: Organized Crime' opposite of Robin Lord Taylor, the final season of 'Bull' on CBS, 2x Emmy winning medieval series 'The Quest' on Disney+, and heavily recurs in the MAX mystery-crime drama, 'Full Circle' by Academy Award winning director, Steven Soderbergh.
